{"tid":2062943,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[開電視］茶餐廳龍虎榜 星期六晚2130-2200","createTime":"2020-06-13T13:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T07:02:12.000Z","uid":30,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd3f60d1ec8c83046d8af51bed80efe87eeb288","tid":2062943,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:41:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/177168103171388/posts/545010936387101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F177168103171388%2Fposts%2F545010936387101%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=3ed17cbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/177168103171388/posts/545010936387101/</a><br />\n<br />\n【邊度嘅雞髀薯條最好味？】<br />\n食茶記代表對嘢食冇要求🤪？傻喇，你以為一底乾濕比例靚嘅乾炒牛河同一碟蛋滑肉嫩嘅滑蛋牛肉飯好易煮㗎？主持張紋嘉Crystal同大家食勻八項茶餐廳必試美食🤤。<br />\n第一味，茶餐！茶餐首選梗係雞髀薯條，Crystal帶埋鄧穎芝Vangie遊走北角同九龍灣試食馳名雞髀，仲會向大廚同老闆偷師。<br />\n再跟煮食KOL Happy Amy嘗試重現茶餐廳風味嘅生炸雞髀。Crystal到底係美女廚神，定係地獄廚神呢？<br />\n<br />\n#香港開電視 #HKOpenTV #開電視 #77台 #茶餐廳龍虎榜 #張紋嘉 #HappyAmy #鄧穎芝 #雞髀薯條"},{"pid":"c8cfb786f2dff05626c922f6bdbdceb3c430850a","tid":2062943,"uid":30,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkopentv/videos/393334194917218/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkopentv%2Fvideos%2F393334194917218%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=7537c7c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkopentv/videos/393334194917218/</a>"},{"pid":"087b6b3b3dd25c6a59f96e56af1715afa35d59cf","tid":2062943,"uid":2811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"幾好睇，推吓po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f5555a39ddbc803b77724d3ace3f92a6e38d6f","tid":2062943,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor